Definition: an ultra-leftist militant group founded in 1957 from the breakup of the Japanese Communist Party
Example: includes a covert action wing; Chukaku-Ha attacks tend to cause property damage rather than casualties
Synonyms: terrorist_organization, i, noun, act, terrorism, c, location, Japan, r, an, ultra-leftist, militant, group, founded, in, from, the, breakup, of, Japanese, Communist, Party, includes, a, covert, action, wing, attacks, tend, to, cause, property, damage, rather, than, casualties
Category: noun.group
